          ></span>
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li data-t>whatIsRaha.parliamentBudget.point1</li>
          <li data-t>whatIsRaha.parliamentBudget.point2</li>
          <li data-t>whatIsRaha.parliamentBudget.point3</li>
          <li data-t>whatIsRaha.parliamentBudget.point4</li>
        </ul>

      </article>
